      "content": "i've tried all that. the \"self-care\" stuff, the talking, the trying to be positive... it just feels like putting a band-aid on a broken limb. it doesn't actually change anything. the loop just resets. i feel like i'm just waiting for the next crash. it's not even a matter of \"feeling better\" anymore, it's just that the repetition is exhausting. i just want it to stop.",
